  <brief_title>Treatment of Vasomotor Symptoms in Korean Post Menopausal Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Multicenter Study Investigating the Efficacy and Tolerability of Angeliq(drospirenon2mg and Estradiol 1mg) in Postmenopausal Korean Women With Vasomotor Symptoms Over 3, 28 Day Treatment Cycle</official_title>
  <sponsors>
