  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study to demonstrate that the therapeutic efficacy of Angeliq® is better than placebo in
      Korean postmenopausal women with hot flushes and other climacteric symptoms. Safety and
      tolerability of Angeliq.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
